{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"author":{"name":"Kingso","contacts":{"twitter":"#"}},"disqusShortname":"kingsoblog","subtitle":"Kingso's blog","title":"Kingso's blog","url":"https://kingso.netlify.com"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"5846d618-a275-5ef3-8be8-4f9e73100923","html":"<br>\n<h2 id=\"03-playing-with-css-variables-and-js\"><a href=\"#03-playing-with-css-variables-and-js\" aria-label=\"03 playing with css variables and js permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>03. Playing with CSS Variables and JS</h2>\n<p>CSS 변수를 사용하여 이미지를 확대 및 축소, 블러 효과, 배경색을 변경할 수 있다.</p>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"목표\"><a href=\"#%EB%AA%A9%ED%91%9C\" aria-label=\"목표 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>목표</h3>\n<p>1.3가지의 input 태그에 대한 CSS 변수를 생성한다.</p>\n<p>2.input 태그의 값이 변경될 때, 뷰를 업데이트 하는 함수 생성</p>\n<p>3.input 태그의 값이 변경될 때마다 함수를 호출한다.</p>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"label-태그\"><a href=\"#label-%ED%83%9C%EA%B7%B8\" aria-label=\"label 태그 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>label 태그</h3>\n<p>label은 폼의 양식에 이름 붙이는 태그입니다. 주요 속성은 for입니다.\nlabel의 for의 값과 양식의 id의 값이 같으면 연결됩니다.</p>\n<p>label을 클릭하면, 연결된 양식에 입력할 수 있도록 하거나 체크를 하거나 체크를 해제합니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"사용자-정의-css-속성-변수-사용하기\"><a href=\"#%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EC%9E%90-%EC%A0%95%EC%9D%98-css-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1-%EB%B3%80%EC%88%98-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"사용자 정의 css 속성 변수 사용하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>사용자 정의 CSS 속성 (변수 사용하기)</h3>\n<p>:root 가상 클래스에 변수를 선언해 놓고, CSS 작성자가 해당 변수를 사용할 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n<span class=\"token selector\">:root</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">--base</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #ffc600<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">--spacing</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">--blur</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">img</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--spacing<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--base<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">blur</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--blur<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/Javascript30-03/","tagSlugs":["/tag/javascript-30/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-07-17T14:00:00.169Z","description":"Playing with CSS Variables and JS","tags":["Javascript30"],"title":"Javascript30 - 03"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/posts/Javascript30-03/"}}